# Project Charter

## Business Objective

Establish a centralized analytics platform that serves as the organization's single source of truth.

## Scope

This engagement will include:

- Analytics architecture
- Data ingestion
- ETL pipeline
- Data warehouse
- KPI definitions
- Executive dashboard

## Out of Scope

- Machine learning
- Forecasting
- Customer segmentation
- Manufacturing optimization

These will be addressed in future engagements.

## Success Metrics

- Reduce manual reporting effort.
- Standardize KPI definitions.
- Deliver automated executive dashboards.
- Improve confidence in business reporting.